Simple BrewFridge controller for Rasperry Pi

To install:

sudo install ruby
sudo install ruby-dev
sudo gem install bundler
{sudo gem install daemons -v '1.1.9'}
sudo install git
git clone https://github.com/markysoft/brewfridge.git
cd to brewfridge
sudo bundle install

to run tests:
rspec -fd

[to update]
git pull origin master
[end]